OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHouse prices grow faster   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthan any calendar year     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsince 2004, Halifax says   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, UK house prices rose at a faster rate  
OL,6, in 2021 than in any calendar year since
OL,7, 2004, according to the Halifax.        
OL,9,FThe mortgage lender said buyers sought 
OL,10,Fmore space during lockdown and took    
OL,11,Fadvantage of low-cost borrowing and    
OL,12,Fstamp duty holidays.                   
OL,14,FPrices increased by 9.8% during 2021,  
OL,15,Fit said - the fastest for any calendar 
OL,16,Fyear since a 12.5% rise in 2004.       
OL,18,FThe average UK property price hit a new
OL,19,Frecord high of #276,091 in December, it
OL,20,Fadded.                                 
